We complement this with a minimal exact comb simulation (small Hilbert spaces, explicit unitaries), confirming the same qualitative behavior with uncertainty bands; see Fig.~\ref{fig:page_curve_exact}. The agreement supports robustness to deviations from Haar-typical scramblers.

